ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知道淋巴欖係咪會變 cancer <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好認真同你講我就係一個淋巴癌 case</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問絲打身體而家健康好嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb2fe064e867e0b5ca9a9de69ccc0e0388609bf","tid":187101,"uid":71694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細佬有淋巴欖 <br />\n家庭醫生話有咩傷風感冒要即睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知道淋巴欖係咪會變 cancer <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好認真同你講我就係一個淋巴癌 case</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問絲打身體而家健康好嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有鳩的，我就係咳咗三個月同有淋巴核腫大，你真係叫你細佬要check清楚"},{"pid":"ac9ee1836a0974473d0b14be3802cc43af5b5e1e","tid":187101,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細佬有淋巴欖 <br />\n家庭醫生話有咩傷風感冒要即睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知道淋巴欖係咪會變 cancer <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好認真同你講我就係一個淋巴癌 case</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問絲打身體而家健康好嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有鳩的，我就係咳咗三個月同有淋巴核腫大，你真係叫你細佬要check清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問巴打可以去邊到 check <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係我鎖骨到有幾粒好細粒 (紅瓜子咁大到)<br />\n家庭醫生話大粒先有問題 <br />\n所以我先冇太理<br />\n<br />\n不過上網睇資料好似好麻煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30322546fc9f13818d38206c779a90eb56013df8","tid":187101,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我有鳩的，我就係咳咗三個月同有淋巴核腫大，你真係叫你細佬要check清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實細佬即是小弟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751f40b4a66f0dcb5d1aa8eb3d0fbeb2657c320c","tid":187101,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:48:00.000Z","msg":"咳到心口側邊有少少痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7585554ecb5be4916431b97042b63a45fcbd2da","tid":187101,"uid":71694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細佬有淋巴欖 <br />\n家庭醫生話有咩傷風感冒要即睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知道淋巴欖係咪會變 cancer <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好認真同你講我就係一個淋巴癌 case</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問絲打身體而家健康好嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有鳩的，我就係咳咗三個月同有淋巴核腫大，你真係叫你細佬要check清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問巴打可以去邊到 check <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係我鎖骨到有幾粒好細粒 (紅瓜子咁大到)<br />\n家庭醫生話大粒先有問題 <br />\n所以我先冇太理<br />\n<br />\n不過上網睇資料好似好麻煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇過好多醫生都無用，最後去政府日間醫療中心叫佢幫我照x光就見到有影就轉介咗去qe。不過有影已經係代表有個瘤大到見到，但見唔到影都唔代表無野可能只係好初期"},{"pid":"48f904415e55d4e3724aa5248f38b88b83234417","tid":187101,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:06:10.000Z","msg":"已經發燒sl左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33352b7f694a383b587a245b72fadfd2e8608056","tid":187101,"uid":9395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a58972c0ef196c1694f6195bc9267b82c8fda82","tid":187101,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"唔戴口罩正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7155c4a186f5e9e28a5d58e09a238a27ad6ee7e2","tid":187101,"uid":6887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:16:47.000Z","msg":"咳到D痰勁深色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁飲水都無好轉"},{"pid":"005dc5dc3e132d01fba7e352877ab52f705eec91","tid":187101,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人係天氣轉氣管敏感先咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdc7b9bdd003934063e99d9f1107876555ae9c9","tid":187101,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"喉嚨痛發燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02adc49018e19d9f58fedfd59e182b73bfb932f","tid":187101,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"1月尾咳到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇左3次醫生 計埋必理痛食左5次藥都好唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf233a31f149e2c8bac20d8c60dd01ff9c12fbc","tid":187101,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細佬有淋巴欖 <br />\n家庭醫生話有咩傷風感冒要即睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知道淋巴欖係咪會變 cancer <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好認真同你講我就係一個淋巴癌 case</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問絲打身體而家健康好嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有鳩的，我就係咳咗三個月同有淋巴核腫大，你真係叫你細佬要check清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問巴打可以去邊到 check <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係我鎖骨到有幾粒好細粒 (紅瓜子咁大到)<br />\n家庭醫生話大粒先有問題 <br />\n所以我先冇太理<br />\n<br />\n不過上網睇資料好似好麻煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇過好多醫生都無用，最後去政府日間醫療中心叫佢幫我照x光就見到有影就轉介咗去qe。不過有影已經係代表有個瘤大到見到，但見唔到影都唔代表無野可能只係好初期</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問巴打點樣發現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b45e481f784cff85c6b67aa93c0fa3c9b53974c","tid":187101,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴絲打小心 <br />\n如果咳左個零兩個禮拜 <br />\n<br />\n你條頸可能會生淋巴核 <br />\n通常醫生摸你頸就係 check 呢樣野 <br />\n<br />\n害處仲查證緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7594d57b36ebc5bf297a6d1064edef90ddca74ea","tid":187101,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"咳左接近成個月 都唔識好"},{"pid":"3be9d365e125629a176a99df161f960365ddc664","tid":187101,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咳左接近成個月 都唔識好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n病完好番幾日, 又感冒, 感冒完又咳, 咳幾日又感眉, 之後又咳<br />\n無撚限LOOP"},{"pid":"ea215f1a279fa433c5e6dbd19d06ff1797ddd42c","tid":187101,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:52:42.000Z","msg":"exact7y<br />\n我去睇醫生，個姑娘都咳緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab6eeb6e89999312903ff406a88077eed1a334a","tid":187101,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"咳左三十日"},{"pid":"f36a2b796d1a0aafd582504ae0aa41c6c316069d","tid":187101,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"感冒完咳左成個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}